    {
      "id": "6f4c5911-d724-459d-bcfe-74e71ef2148c",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Authors follow-up by attempting to improve the original model by pre-classifying the different videos according to the content - theoretical, experimental and/or analytical. The creation of different models shows that by model performance is relatively unaffected if the models only consider theoretical and experimental videos. ",
